1: His previous VA, Maddie Blaustein was Jewish, and his current VA could be paying homage to her.

2: Or his current VA is Jewish as well!

title: Pokemon Trading and Breeding
body:
I love to breed competitive pokemon, so I thought I’d start a blog for it. If you want a specific pokemon, tell me:

Species, Gender, Ability, IVs, EVs, Nature, Pokeball, and if you want it shiny

And I’ll go ahead and get it done for you. When I’m done, I’ll pm you for your friend code and when we can get together to get it to you. Don’t forget to have a throwaway poke for the trade.

I’m also interested in trading, so if you have any trades, I’ll set up a link to my poke spreadsheet.

summary: "You're made of gold right? why don't we just smelt some down into a nice little coin you can give me for some food?"
question: "You're made of gold right? why don't we just smelt some down into a nice little coin you can give me for some food?"
answer:
“I’m not using myself to pay for food. That’s almost like selling your kidney to get money for some chicken nuggets.

“Now I really want nuggies…”
